DeviceAccessor version 0.01
===========================

Perl XS module created to provide a wrapper around the functionality available
within the libudev.h library. The core functionality is to allow for searching
of devices and information retrieval (e.g. device name, filesystem path).

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  libudev-dev

